'''Khilaafada Raashidiinta''' ama '''Dawladii khulafada raashidiinta''' (afka [[Carabi|carabiga]];'''الخِلافةُ الرَّاشِدَة, دولةُ الخُلَفاءِ الرَّاشِدين''') waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[Khilaafada Islaamka|khilaafadii]] ugu horeeyay ee islaamaka, taas oo bilaabatay geerida [[Nebi Maxamed c.s|rasuulka scw]] ka dib sanadkii [[11H]], socotayna ilaa [[Mucawiya|mucaawiya]] ay khilaafada u guurtay 41H, waxaana xilka qabtay afarta khulafa ee kala ah [[Abu Bakr|Abuubakar sidiiq]], [[Cumar (saxaaba)|Cumar bin Khadaab]], [[Cusmaan bin Cafaan|Cusmaan bin cafaan]] iyo [[Cali|Cali bin Abii daalib]], kwaasi oo loo yaqaan [[khulafada raashidiinta]], mararka qaar waxaa lagu daraa [[Xasan ibn Cali|Xasan bin cali]] oo loo arko muadada yareed uu xilka haayay inay dhameestiraysay afartii ka horeysay.
{{Template:Khaliif}}'''Khulafo Raashidiin'''  ({{lang-en|Rashidun Caliphates}}; (sidoo kale loo yaaqaano: '''[[Rashidiinta]]''', '''[[Afarta Khulafo]]''') waa [[afartii asxaabi]] ee ku xigtey [[Nebi Muxamed]] (n.n.k.h) maamulka iyo hogaanka dawladii [[Islaam|Islaamka]], kuwaasi oo kala ah:

* [[Abu Bakr Sadiiq]] - '''ﺃﺑﻮ ﺑﻜﺮ ﺍﻟﺼﺪﻳﻖ'''
* [[Cumar]] (Cumar bin Khataab) - '''ﻋﻤﺮ ﺑﻦ ﺍﻟﺨﻄﺎﺏ'''
* [[Cusmaan binu Cafaan]] - '''ﻋﺜﻤﺎﻥ ﺑﻦ ﻋﻔﺎﻥ''' iyo
* [[Cali]] (Cali binu abi Dalib) - '''ﻋﻠﻲ ﺑﻦ ﺃﺑﻲ ﻃﺎﻟﺐ'''

Ereyga Khaliif (Caliph; ﺍﻟﺨﻼﻓﺔ) waa khaliifyadii hogaaminayay [[Diin|maamulka diinta]] [[Islaam|Islaamka]].

[[Khaliif|Khulafo al-Rashiidiintu]] waa [[Afar|afarta asxaabi]] ee hogaanka iyo talada maamulka Dawladda [[Islaam|Islaamka]] la waday [[Nebi Muxamed SCW]] intii uu noolaa isla markaana gacanta ku dhigay ayagoo iskaga dambeeyay hogaaminta dowladii Islaamka. Wakhtigii Khulafo al Raashidiinta Dawladda Islaamku aad ayay u balaadhatay waxayna gaadhay meelo badan oo ka mid ah [[Bariga Dhexe]], [[Yurub|galbeedka qaarada Yurub]], [[Afrika|waqooyiga Afrika]], [[Aasiya|bariga fog]] iyo wadano aad u badan oo kale. 

Wakhtigani maamulka Dawladda Islaamka ee [[Afarta Khulafo]] wuxuu bilaabmey [[Bil|8dii Juune]] [[Sanad|sanadkii 632 C.D]]; wuxuuna dhamaadaa [[Wakhti|28 Luuliyo]] [[Sanad|sanadkii 661 C.D]] taasi oo ku beegan goortii la dilay [[Cali|Cali binu Abi Dalib]] ee xilka iyo hogaanka Dawladda Islaamka uu la wareegay [[Mucaawiya|Mucaawiya binu Abi Sufyaan]]. 
Intii [[Afarta Khulafo]] talada Dawladda Islaamka hayeen waxay qabsadeen dhu aad u baaxad weynt taasi oo lagu qiyaaso [[Km|9,000,000 km²]] ([[9|sagaal milyan mitir laba-laaban]])
(3,474,919 sq mi). 
Tirada dadka ku hoos jirey maamulka iyo hogaanka [[Khaliif|Khulafo al-Raashidiinta]] waxaa lagu sheegaa [[Milyan|40,300,000]] (qiyaas dhan [[40|40 milyan]] oo qof).
